High throughput proteomics identifies a high-accuracy 11 plasma protein 
biomarker signature for ovarian cancer.

Enroth S(#)(1), Berggrund M(#)(1), Lycke M(2), Broberg J(3), Lundberg M(3), 
Assarsson E(3), Olovsson M(4), Stålberg K(4), Sundfeldt K(2), Gyllensten U(1).

Author information:
(1)1Department of Immunology, Genetics, and Pathology, Biomedical Center, 
Science for Life Laboratory (SciLifeLab) Uppsala, Box 815, Uppsala University, 
SE-75108 Uppsala, Sweden.
(2)2Department of Obstetrics and Gynaecology, Institute of Clinical Sciences, 
